'''天主教波托維耶霍總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Portus Veteris}}；{{lang-es|Arquidiócesis de Portoviejo}}）是[[厄瓜多爾|厄瓜多爾]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄一個教區。此總教區是該國四個總教區之一。

==歷史==
波托維耶霍教區於1870年3月23日設立，1994年2月25日升為總教區。

==現況==
總教區位於[[馬納維省|馬納維省]]，2004年時有教友1,091,143人（佔轄區總人口92.0%）、七十八個堂區和116名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-de|愛德華·若瑟·卡斯蒂略-皮諾|Eduardo José Castillo Pino}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 02.10.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/02/191002d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002131724/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/02/191002d.html |archivedate=2019-10-02 |language=en |date=2019-10-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|雲先·歐拉西奧·賽特羅斯-謝拉|Vicente Horacio Saeteros Sierra}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 16.05.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/16/200516c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521122129/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/16/200516c.html |archivedate=2020-05-21 |language=en |date=2020-05-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-de|若瑟·瑪略·魯伊斯-納瓦斯|José Mario Ruiz Navas}}和{{link-it|老楞佐·沃爾托利尼-埃斯蒂|Lorenzo Voltolini Esti|老楞佐·沃爾托利尼}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 06.08.2007 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2007/08/06/0417/01122.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002135044/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2007/08/06/0417/01122.html |archivedate=2019-10-02 |language=it |date=2007-08-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 14.09.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/09/14/180914c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002134435/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018